Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擊必殺格鬥技
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是金星人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是荒川之主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是荒川之主二代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追  跟丟了就不能打分了
