Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然少女的夢想就是當花嫁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花嫁  P子你想嫁給花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.78,0:23:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你最喜歡的人是花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我喜歡的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  第8橋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的人是！
